task_description: Navigate to Bristo Place. Start on Forrest Road and bear right at the fork to stay on the main road, keeping the National Museum on your right. Continue straight, passing Sandy Bell's pub on the left. At the junction with the traffic lights, turn left onto Bristo Place.

reason: There is only one available move forward to begin the navigation along Forrest Road.
